STATE of North Carolina
v.
Benji COLLINS. No. 430P05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. August 18, 2005. William P. Hart, Special Deputy Attorney General, William David McFadyen, Jr., District Attorney, for State of NC.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 10th day of August 2005 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the Superior Court, Craven County, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court of that County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 18th day of August 2005."
